⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⣴⠖⠚⠛⠒⠶⠦⣤⡾⠋⠙⣦⣤⣤⣤⡴⠚⢳⡀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⢠⠟⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠘⠃⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠘⣇⠀
⠀⠀⣠⡟⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢸⡆
⣸⠋⠟⡀⠀⠀⢀⡀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢧⣤⠆⢀⡀⢠⣤⡤⢸⡇
⠹⣄⠀⠙⠛⠛⠉⠉⠹⣧⠀⠚⠓⢦⡀⠀⠀⠈⠉⠀⠀⢠⣿⡄
⠀⠀⠙⢳⢦⣤⣤⣤⢴⡿⡳⠶⢤⣤⡼⣷⠦⢤⣤⣤⡤⡴⣿⠞⠃
⠀⠀⠀⠁⠊⠁⠈⠈⠁⠀⠀⠈⠁⠉⠀⠁⠀⠉⠐⠁⠉⠀⠀⠀`;
---

<section class="sleepyCat" aria-hidden="true">
	<p class="prompt">[~/home]$ nap --now<span class="cursor">_</span></p>
	<div class="scene">
		<pre class="cat">{CAT_ART}</pre>
		<span class="z z1">z</span>
		<span class="z z2">Z</span>
		<span class="z z3">Zz</span>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.sleepyCat {
		margin: 0 0 0.55rem;
		display: grid;
		justify-items: center;
		gap: 0.35rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
	}

	.prompt {
		margin: 0;
		font-family: var(--mono);
		font-size: 0.64rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		text-transform: lowercase;
		color: var(--muted);
		opacity: 0.92;
	}

	.cursor {
		display: inline-block;
		margin-left: 0.04rem;
		color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 65%, var(--text-secondary));
		animation: cursorBlink 1s steps(1, end) infinite;
	}

	.scene {
		position: relative;
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.05rem 0;
		max-width: 100%;
	}

	.cat {
		margin: 0;
		font-family: var(--mono);
		font-size: clamp(0.37rem, 0.95vw, 0.5rem);
		line-height: 1.02;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		white-space: pre;
		background: transparent;
		border: 0;
		padding: 0;
		border-radius: 0;
		box-shadow: none;
		overflow-x: auto;
		scrollbar-width: none;
		animation: catBreath 2.3s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	.cat::-webkit-scrollbar {
		display: none;
	}

	.z {
		position: absolute;
		left: 56%;
		top: 0.14rem;
		font-family: var(--mono);
		color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--accent) 45%, var(--text-secondary));
		opacity: 0;
		animation: zDrift 2.9s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	.z2 {
		left: 59%;
		font-size: 0.92em;
		animation-delay: 0.95s;
	}

	.z3 {
		left: 62%;
		font-size: 0.84em;
		animation-delay: 1.9s;
	}

	@keyframes catBreath {
		0%,
		100% {
			transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg);
		}
		50% {
			transform: translateY(2px) rotate(0.35deg);
		}
	}

	@keyframes zDrift {
		0%,
		14% {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateY(0) translateX(0) scale(0.95);
		}
		28%,
		62% {
			opacity: 0.82;
		}
		100% {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateY(-1.1rem) translateX(0.35rem) scale(1.06);
		}
	}

	@keyframes cursorBlink {
		0%,
		48% {
			opacity: 1;
		}
		49%,
		100% {
			opacity: 0;
		}
	}

	@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
		.cat,
		.z {
			animation: none;
		}

		.z {
			opacity: 0;
		}

		.z1 {
			opacity: 0.46;
			transform: translateY(-0.25rem);
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 740px) {
		.cat {
			font-size: clamp(0.33rem, 1.55vw, 0.42rem);
		}

		.z {
			left: 54%;
			top: 0.08rem;
		}

		.z2 {
			left: 57%;
		}

		.z3 {
			left: 60%;
		}
	}
</style>
